  "title": "中科院3区、可持续计算期刊：IEEE T-SUSC",
  "author": "tianhe",
  "digest": "助力学术成长，点亮科研之路",
  "show_cover_pic": 1,
  "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><section style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px\"><h1 id=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 1em; border-bottom: 2px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em auto 1em; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0\" data-heading=\"true\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">璇玑枢，助力学术成长，点亮科研之路</strong></h1><section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">  <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"璇玑枢\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQiaFnHeBCs7xpwn7nA5icgHYLcsrWEbajjxSLMRBhIhhFqj8m9VSAP0vkAcnS2O3PbKUic5H1M2xKpDicyUic7d2iaqvJiaVDZWiacaLfQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"期刊介绍，论文润色，深度学习，人工智能\" data-id=\"MzY4OTE0NjQwMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"2\">  </mp-common-profile></section><section>  <span leaf=\"\"><br></span></section><p style=\"display: none;\">  <mp-style-type data-value=\"3\">  </mp-style-type></p><section style=\"background:#f3f3f3;padding:18px 20px 14px 20px;margin:16px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.6;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none;display: inline-block;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzY4OTE0NjQwMA==&mid=2247485611&idx=1&sn=e1f0e99a075476bd4b9e4ad40a3adccf&source=41&poc_token=HLtbuWmjCxPZuZHXYo-qKhtwRiz7oN3d1HegSgJG\" textvalue=\"科研期刊分类合集（持续更新）\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">科研期刊分类合集（持续更新）</a></span><section style=\"width:72px;height:3px;background:#2b6ff2;margin:10px 0 12px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></section><section style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#9aa0a6;\"><span leaf=\"\">合集对已介绍的多本科研期刊按研究方向与期刊定位进行汇总与分类。</span></section></section><figure style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"null\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQjoTJ55MTv4CKy3h5GU3dAhnICp44kETjGey555Tpxp22fjqCfGkQMq8oVl6lbQcBPACAcO244KZIKicRBOv9X7UJW24s2o4EPI/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px\"><figcaption style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Sustainable Computing（T-SUSC）</strong> 是由 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Computer Society / IEEE</strong> 出版的国际学术期刊，主要面向 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">可持续计算理论、系统架构、软硬件协同优化与绿色应用技术</strong> 等研究领域。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">该期刊致力于推动 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">面向能源效率、资源节约、环境友好与可持续发展的计算技术研究</strong>，覆盖从 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">软件、硬件设计到系统与应用实现</strong> 的完整技术链条，是可持续计算方向具有明确主题定位的 IEEE Transactions 期刊之一。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">T-SUSC 的核心定位非常明确：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">发表围绕 sustainable computing 的原创研究成果，强调计算系统在性能、能耗、资源利用与环境影响之间的综合优化</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">在可持续计算研究体系中，IEEE Transactions on Sustainable Computing 通常被视为 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">绿色计算、节能系统与可持续智能基础设施研究的重要学术期刊</strong>，其整体定位大致相当于：</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">可持续计算与绿色系统研究领域的重要 Transactions 期刊</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">从当前期刊状态看，T-SUSC 已形成较清晰的主题辨识度，但整体影响力仍更接近 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">稳定发展的专业方向期刊</strong>，而不是大体量的综合旗舰刊。近几年其影响因子经历波动后回升至 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.9</strong>，说明该刊在可持续计算、绿色 AI、节能系统与低碳基础设施等方向仍保持持续关注度，但竞争格局也更依赖选题与研究完成度。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">长期以来，该期刊被 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">SCIE / Scopus</strong> 收录，并在 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">中科院期刊分区（2025年3月最新升级版）</strong> 中位于 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机科学大类 3区</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">期刊官网：https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/RecentIssue.jsp?punumber=7274860</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">Index：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">SCIE / Scopus</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">期刊类型：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">研究类文章为主（Research Articles 为主体）</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">开放获取：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">No（非 OA）</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">学科分区（以页面最新说明为准）：<ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• JCR（2024-2025 最新版）：</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">COMPUTER SCIENCE, HARDWARE & ARCHITECTURE：Q2</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">COMPUTER SCIENCE, INFORMATION SYSTEMS：Q2</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">TELECOMMUNICATIONS：Q2</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 中科院期刊分区（2025年3月最新升级版）：</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">大类：计算机科学 3区</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">小类：COMPUTER SCIENCE, HARDWARE & ARCHITECTURE 3区；COMPUTER SCIENCE, INFORMATION SYSTEMS 3区；TELECOMMUNICATIONS 3区</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">Top 期刊：否；综述期刊：否</strong></li></ul></p><figure style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"null\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQjfDgjficKKLzlh3iarICaFLql7uQ4UStY4SHteRB21Hkrw24PyEl5VE2gCl8WsAc0lvJZoMAh6lWd6s4I52ZDHGpuibYlnV5sZCc/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px\"><figcaption style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\"></figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">近期影响力与学术地位</h2><figure style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"null\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQgBIA8xawMsQTibpwBMiawl8kl5oj84erfBU8W4b1ibFn6426S8pWdXGT9datqsfL3zvYaMbLiakxbJjf3gvSXTFAIKoH4wa6FvvlY/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px\"><figcaption style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">从最新指标来看，<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Sustainable Computing 在可持续计算与绿色系统研究领域具有一定学术影响力</strong>，相关论文在 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">能耗优化、绿色数据中心、可持续 AI、资源感知系统设计与绿色网络计算</strong> 等方向具有持续引用价值。结合当前公开信息看，该刊的现状更适合概括为：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">方向特色鲜明、体量适中、影响力稳定恢复中</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">其最新核心指标为：<ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Impact Factor（2024-2025）：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.9</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• CiteScore：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">8</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Eigenfactor：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">0.00153</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Article Influence Score：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">0.742</strong></li></ul></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">这些指标表明，该期刊在 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">绿色计算与可持续信息系统领域</strong> 具有稳定但相对专业化的国际学术影响力。与计算机领域更高位次的综合强刊相比，T-SUSC 的优势不在于绝对指标高度，而在于 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">“可持续计算”主题聚焦明确，适合绿色系统与节能优化方向的针对性投稿</strong>。</p><h2 id=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">发文情况</h2><figure style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"null\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQjJNYUL0sooNJJmEyiabOrbTGSHMf9akjZS6wFrib4sJbFActjGWnriatr8n2hdnSg6ZSYKia9capIDPAicDSGcpe3ZX8qDYgSajMOk/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px\"><figcaption style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">从近年来的出版情况来看，T-SUSC 的发文规模相对适中：<ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 年文章数：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">70（2024–2025 年度）</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 期刊发文类型：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">研究论文为主</strong></li></ul></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">从当前趋势看，期刊年发文量不算大，但近几年已形成稳定输出。这意味着 T-SUSC 更像是 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">围绕可持续计算主题持续积累高相关研究成果的专业型期刊平台</strong>，而不是依赖超大发文量扩张影响力的刊物。对于作者而言，这类期刊通常更看重 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">选题与期刊主题的匹配度</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">随着绿色计算与低碳数字基础设施的发展，该期刊在 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">能效优化、绿色云与边缘计算、可持续 AI 加速、资源受限系统设计</strong> 等方向的研究成果持续增加。</p><h2 id=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">征稿范围</h2><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Sustainable Computing（T-SUSC）</strong> 主要关注 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">可持续计算理论、系统与应用研究</strong>，包括但不限于以下方向：<h3 id=\"6\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">一、可持续计算体系结构与平台</h3><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 绿色计算体系结构</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 节能型软硬件协同设计</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 可持续数据中心与计算平台</li></ul><h3 id=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">二、资源管理与能效优化</h3><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 能耗感知资源调度</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 性能—功耗—碳排放协同优化</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 资源受限环境下的系统优化</li></ul><h3 id=\"8\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">三、可持续计算应用与服务</h3><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 绿色云计算与边缘计算</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 可持续人工智能与机器学习系统</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 面向环境与社会可持续发展的计算应用</li></ul><h3 id=\"9\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">四、绿色网络与基础设施</h3><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 绿色通信与网络系统</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 低碳物联网与智能基础设施</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 可持续计算场景下的系统评估方法</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">期刊强调 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">从软件、硬件设计到应用实现的全链条可持续计算研究</strong>，鼓励研究成果在 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">真实系统平台、能耗测评环境或资源约束场景</strong> 中进行验证。结合当前选题趋势，<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">仅有一般性能改进而缺乏“可持续性”核心贡献</strong> 的论文，往往不如同时体现 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">节能、资源效率或环境价值</strong> 的工作更匹配该刊。</p><h2 id=\"4\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">投稿建议</h2><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 强调 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">能效优化、资源利用或可持续性指标上的原创贡献</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 提供 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">真实平台实验、能耗测试或系统级评估验证</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 在论文中体现 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">性能、功耗、碳效率或资源效率的综合提升</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 在结构上保持 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">问题定义清晰、方法严谨、实验可复现</strong></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">投稿系统：https://mc.manuscriptcentral.com/tsusc-cs</p><h2 id=\"5\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">期刊总结</h2>总体来看，<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Sustainable Computing（T-SUSC）</strong> 是 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">可持续计算、绿色系统与节能信息基础设施研究领域具有明确方向特色的 IEEE Transactions 期刊之一</strong>。<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">凭借 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Computer Society 的出版背景与可持续计算主题的持续升温</strong>，该期刊持续汇聚 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">绿色云与边缘计算、节能系统优化、可持续 AI 与绿色网络基础设施</strong> 等方向的研究成果。就当前现状而言，它更适合定位为 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">主题明确、学科交叉性强、影响力稳步恢复中的专业研究平台</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">在可持续计算研究社区中，T-SUSC 仍然是 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">具有代表性的高水平绿色计算研究期刊平台之一</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">璇玑枢，我以渺小，与你同行——愿你的绿色系统设计与可持续计算研究，在每一次优化与验证中更接近长期价值。</strong></p></section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/pdoYWlyPiaWE88Y687KoLpQPXSw646ISBHAUmLDZ1Hk9YxnuC551yF9ibpLiaLK4NyqNO15icJvZdsic5HqMUNJQwNg/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p>",
